It's simple assignment for advanced internet appliacations ;-)
"Flex grid" is based on css @media only screen and (min width: x) and (max-width: y)
and setting necessary elements width using percentages.
To create sticky footer I group all other content in one div and assign to it style class
with min-height: 100% and margin-bottom equals negative footer height.
I decide to make menu button's position fixed and display menu list after this button is hover.
To enable article's wrapping it needs to use flex-wrap: wrap.
Most of the content has flex display.
